OL,6,FA north Wales woman who has been
OL,7,Fliving in a hotel for 17 weeks after
OL,8,Fher home was flooded during Storm
OL,9,FBabet says her family has lost
OL,10,F"everything".
OL,12,FMany schools were closed due to the
OL,13,Fheavy rain and flooding in the region
OL,14,Fwhen Babet swept across the UK.
OL,16,FJudith Owen from said: "As a family
OL,17,Fwe've been living in a hotel now for
OL,18,F17 weeks and we're hoping to be back
OL,19,Fin, hopefully, in the next couple of
OL,20,Fmonths.
