OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We know it is
OL,7,Fnot possible to stop or prevent all
OL,8,Fflooding and coastal erosion, but we
OL,9,Fcan and are indeed taking steps to
OL,10,Freduce the consequences and help
OL,11,Fcreate more resilient communities
OL,12,Facross Wales.
OL,14,F"The installation of sustainable urban
OL,15,Fdrainage systems (SUDS) and other
OL,16,Fnatural flood management helps slow
OL,17,Fdown run off and helps reduce
OL,18,Fpollution, and we continue to support
OL,19,Fwater industry campaigns to prevent
OL,20,Fthe flushing of anything other than
OL,21,Ftoilet paper into the sewerage system."
