OL,6,FKeith Ivens, Natural Resources Wales
OL,7,F(NRW) Operations Manager, Flood and
OL,8,FWater Management, said: "Managing
OL,9,Fflood risk in some areas is more
OL,10,Fcomplex than in others and it is
OL,11,Fimportant that we work closely with
OL,12,Fpartners, such as Flintshire County
OL,13,FCouncil in this instance, to reduce
OL,14,Frisk in communities through routine
OL,15,Fmaintenance programmes, and in
OL,16,Fdeveloping business case plans for
OL,17,Fimprovement works that require capital
OL,18,Finvestment funding from Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment.
