OL,6,F"Private landowners also have a part
OL,7,Fto play. If you own land or property
OL,8,Fnext to a river, stream or ditch you
OL,9,Fare therefore a 'riparian landowner'
OL,10,Fwith certain rights and
OL,11,Fresponsibilities in connection to the
OL,12,Fwater flowing through your land. We
OL,13,Fhave produced a guidance document that
OL,14,Fis available on our website with added
OL,15,Finformation."
